<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Simulador Universitario - Polinomios y Funciones</title>

<style>
body{
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background:#f4f6f9;
    margin:0;
    padding:20px;
}

.container{
    max-width:1200px;
    margin:auto;
    background:white;
    padding:30px;
    border-radius:12px;
